metadata.description: Small dataset with 1000 samples to test few shot generation. Uses manually procured eval set.

samples.instruction: The following describes a reaction system. Please translate to a formal description. Mfn is eradicated. It leaves the system with a rate of 8.98. Mfn undergoes a reaction resulting in CaN.

The following describes a reaction system. Please translate to a formal description. When distressed female Tortoise and male distressed Tortoise mate, they produce a pup distressed Tortoise as offspring. Distressed Tortoise, stressed Shark, and stressed Raccoon die.

The following describes a reaction system. Please translate to a formal description. RPS16B, Fis1, and ENO2 are destroyed. A chain of reactions occurs from ENO2 through RPS16B to finally form PMA1. The enymatic reaction from PMA1 to RPS16B with a rate of 3.03 is catalyzed by Fis1. PMA1 and RPS16B are destroyed.

The following describes a reaction system. Please translate to a formal description. A distressed Shark may leave the system. The rate of distressed Shark leaving the system is 6.08. Sick Raccoon emerges in the system. The rate of sick Raccoon entering the system is 8.57. Furthermore, a sick Raccoon may leave the system. Distressed Shark and sated Tortoise undergo a predation to yield distressed Shark.

The following describes a reaction system. Please translate to a formal description. Tortoise, Shark, and sick Raccoon die. Shark, sick Raccoon, and Tortoise can enter the system. Moreover, Shark and sick Raccoon undergo a predation to yield Shark. Shark, Tortoise, and sick Raccoon die.

The following describes a reaction system. Please translate to a formal description. A diseased Tortoise may leave the system. The rate of diseased Tortoise leaving the system is 2.19. Raccoon emerges in the system. The rate of Raccoon entering the system is 3.73.

The following describes a reaction system. Please translate to a formal description. A healthy Shark may leave the system. The rate of healthy Shark leaving the system is 1.97. Raccoon emerges in the system. The rate of Raccoon entering the system is 8.23. Tortoise are hunted by Raccoon with a rate of 3.7. A Raccoon may leave the system. The rate of Raccoon leaving the system is 9.64.
